      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that exceeds conventional expectations. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a masterfully maintained specimen that performs with the precision and grace of a new vehicle. Available for immediate acquisition.",
