    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, you'd think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been totally babied, kept in a garage, and it still has that 'new car' feel every time you get behind the wheel. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come check it out\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
