    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_21",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo represents the pinnacle of 90s grand touring performance. It features the iconic 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six, utilizing its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration for a linear power band and exceptional thermal efficiency. The drivetrain is anchored by the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec Torsen limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original double-wishbone architecture, providing surgical precision and optimal contact patches. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting factory-original internals, a pristine cooling system, and a completely stock exhaust path. It is a true collector\u2019s piece for the purist who demands uncompromised mechanical integrity.",
